ARE YOU DOING ENOUGH?

You’re not tired, you’re just comfortable. That’s the truth. Every time you settle for less, you’re choosing comfort over growth. I’ve been there, making excuses, waiting for the ‘right’ moment. But here’s the thing – the right moment doesn’t come, you have to create it. 

The grind is hard, the progress is slow, but quitting guarantees nothing. Push past the doubt, push past the excuses. This is where real change begins.

Pretty sure, 99% of the people don’t even think about the consequences of what they do on their daily basis. 

Because obviously, it’s not going to impact them in the short term. It’s hard to visualise what will the impact be for doing the same action repetitively over multiple years?

But guess what, whenever you go and watch history, you will realise that every person who has made it big in life, was thinking for the long-term. He knew the long-term consequences of the actions that he was taking that day.

You can get ahead of 99% of the people by just asking this one question to yourself. What will be the consequence of this particular action? Will it help me grow? Will it ruin my future will develop my personality.

99% of the people are going to watch this and scroll away. You still have a chance to get ahead of them. Keep Grinding.
